    <title>Flutter ListTile 自定义垂直边距、标题与两边的水平间距</title>
    <link href="http://www.playhi.net/2020/03/15/Flutter-ListTile-%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E8%BE%B9%E8%B7%9D%E3%80%81%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%A4%E8%BE%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D/"/>
    <id>http://www.playhi.net/2020/03/15/Flutter-ListTile-%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E8%BE%B9%E8%B7%9D%E3%80%81%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%A4%E8%BE%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D/</id>
    <published>2020-03-15T11:54:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-23T10:26:33.715Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>自定义 Flutter ListTile <code>minVerticalPadding</code> 最小垂直边距、<code>horizontalTitleGap</code> 标题与两边的水平间距。</p><a id="more"></a><ol><li>引入依赖 <a href="https://pub.dev/packages/list_tile_more_customizable" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pub.dev:list_tile_more_customizable</a>：<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">dependencies:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">list_tile_more_customizable:</span> <span class="string">^1.2.1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li>将需要处的 <code>ListTile</code> 替换成 <code>ListTileMoreCustomizable</code>，即可直接修改 <code>minVerticalPadding</code>、<code>horizontalTitleGap</code> 以修改相应的值：<figure class="highlight dart"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 类似于</span></span><br><span class="line">ListTileMoreCustomizable(</span><br><span class="line">    title: Text(<span class="string">"标题"</span>),</span><br><span class="line">    horizontalTitleGap: <span class="number">0.0</span>, <span class="comment">// 标题与两边的水平间距</span></span><br><span class="line">    minVerticalPadding: <span class="number">0.0</span>, <span class="comment">// 最小垂直边距</span></span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li></ol><p><a href="https://pub.dev/packages/list_tile_more_customizable" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pub.dev 地址</a><br><a href="https://github.com/Playhi/list_tile_more_customizable" target="_blank" rel="noopener">源码 GitHub 地址</a></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;自定义 Flutter ListTile &lt;code&gt;minVerticalPadding&lt;/code&gt; 最小垂直边距、&lt;code&gt;horizontalTitleGap&lt;/code&gt; 标题与两边的水平间距。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
