    <title>Flutter 实现点击控件后在对应位置弹出 Menu 菜单</title>
    <link href="http://www.playhi.net/2020/02/22/Flutter-%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E6%8E%A7%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%8E%E5%9C%A8%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%BC%B9%E5%87%BA-Menu-%E8%8F%9C%E5%8D%95/"/>
    <id>http://www.playhi.net/2020/02/22/Flutter-%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E6%8E%A7%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%8E%E5%9C%A8%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%BC%B9%E5%87%BA-Menu-%E8%8F%9C%E5%8D%95/</id>
    <published>2020-02-22T11:51:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-23T10:26:33.787Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Flutter 实现点击控件后在对应位置弹出 Menu 菜单</p><a id="more"></a><p>先上图：<br><img src="/images/postsImgs/Screenshot_1582374460.png" alt="效果图"></p><p>直入主题，直接贴关键代码：</p><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">GestureDetector(</span><br><span class="line">  child: <span class="comment">//Child,</span></span><br><span class="line">  onLongPressStart: (details) { <span class="comment">// 一般的 onLongPress 没有位置信息，所以套了一个 GestureDetector </span></span><br><span class="line">    showMenu(</span><br><span class="line">      context: context,</span><br><span class="line">      position: RelativeRect.fromLTRB(</span><br><span class="line">        details.globalPosition.dx,</span><br><span class="line">        details.globalPosition.dy,</span><br><span class="line">        details.globalPosition.dx,</span><br><span class="line">        details.globalPosition.dy,</span><br><span class="line">      ),</span><br><span class="line">      items: &lt;PopupMenuEntry&gt;[</span><br><span class="line">        PopupMenuItem(child: Text(<span class="string">"123"</span>)), <span class="comment">// Menu Item</span></span><br><span class="line">      ],</span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">  },</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>如果要单击而不是长按实现的话，把 onLongPressStart 换成 onTapUp 就有了。</p>]]></content>
    
